{"tid":169325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方為選舉日演習示威衝突　施放催淚彈、棍毆示威者","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T06:36:20.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3245760e67eb83e86e8e02a79787e3e38ca49b","tid":169325,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-training_L1Trf_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-training_L1Trf_1200x0.png&h=07038ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因應選管會篩選候選人令選舉主任受到恐嚇的民情，警方預計於周日立法會選舉投票日，出動最少4,000至5,000警力戒備，近日更多次進行大規模演練，模擬與示威者的衝突，當中不乏施放催淚彈及出動「速龍隊」以警棍等制服示威者的場面。<br />\n<br />\n過千名機動部隊人員昨今兩日在粉嶺機動部隊基地演練。模擬有手持雨傘的示威者，先在行人路聲援小販，食環署人員被包圍，警方到場協助他們離開，但示威者之後衝出佔領馬路，並投擲物品。警方舉紅旗警告後，施放胡椒噴霧驅趕，又模擬清場期間有示威者佩戴安全帽、口罩，手持自製盾牌及木棍對峙。<br />\n<br />\n無綫新聞的片段可見，警方先施放催淚彈驅散示威者，更出動俗稱「速龍隊」的特別戰術小隊，以警棍狂毆並制服穿著全套護甲的示威者。雖未見有水炮車，但見警員持水炮向示威者狂噴。演練並模擬有示威者縱火，在場警員如何應對。  <br />\n<br />\n警務處副處長周國良、行動處處長劉業成等管理層到場觀察演習，是年初二旺角暴動後進行裝備，編制及行動檢討後，首次有警隊高層實地觀察新的應變措施。無綫新聞引述警方消息指，9月4日立法會投票日，全港500多個票站以及亞洲博覽館點票中心，都會有警員駐守。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步計劃會在正常人力外，部署總部以及5個總區，共6支應變大隊，連同後備應急的衝鋒隊以及水警人員，額外警力將超過4,000人。另外，1,500名輔警亦將奉召執勤。  <br />\n<br />\n報道引引述有關消息指，警方情報顯示，投票當日預計不會有大型動亂，但個別地區可能會因應選情激烈有零星衝突，警方會在個別地區重點布防及監控。警隊指揮中心會在選舉當日清晨6時開始運作，至翌日全部選舉結果公布後。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/training5_MeqcX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftraining5_MeqcX_1200x0.png&h=b658a9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/training4_JlS03_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftraining4_JlS03_1200x0.png&h=1c7b8449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/training3_2FS2h_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftraining3_2FS2h_1200x0.png&h=9cfda4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%82%BA%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BE%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%A3%8D%E6%AF%86%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2f1686e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=7ad53502\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%82%BA%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BE%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%A3%8D%E6%AF%86%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/</a>"},{"pid":"483f4e39bf640ba5ec120fa2cca1749511ec2a4a","tid":169325,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}